page.title: 16I am James McColl
page.content: I am a boy.My full name is James Daniel Alistair McColl.But my friends call me"Uggy".I have blondish hair.My eyes are grey in colour.I am about average height.I come from a large family.I have three brothers and one sister who are a lot older than me.They are in their late twenties and early thirties where I am only ten.I have two sisters_in_law and a nephew as well.My nephew is eleven months old.I usually wear cords or jeans and a jumper.I have two cats,one tom cat and one she cat.The tom cat is called Smokey and the she cat is called Stray.My hobbies are bird_watching,trainspotting and football.My favourite football team is Norwich City.John Deehan is my favourite player.
